  <notes>**Component Justification (per CLAUDE.md §11)**: (1) Existing — HandleNarrate currently constructs prompts inline; AnalysisOrchestrationService.RunPlaybookAsync already exists. (2) Extension — Yes; this REPLACES existing implementation by routing through the playbook engine rather than introducing a new service. (3) Cost-of-doing-nothing — Hallucination persists because prompts cannot be iterated without recompile (concrete R3 UAT defect). Wrapper code is the minimal surface. Watch ADR-013 placement — dispatch logic stays in endpoint; orchestration stays in service.</notes>
